==English==

===Noun===
'''H5N1'''

# {{medicine}} A strain of [[avian influenza]], often lethal in humans but not [[transmissible]] between humans.

===Quotations===
2005: At present, H5N1 flu strain poses only a limited threat to humans as it cannot spread easily between people. &mdash; [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/4343136.stm Case of Bird Flu Drug Resistance], BBC Online.

